27:41.500 --> 27:44.080
♪♪

27:44.080 --> 27:46.420
[ Monitor beeps ]

27:46.420 --> 27:48.330
They ended your suspension?

27:48.330 --> 27:50.120
Temporarily. Yeah.

27:50.120 --> 27:56.460
♪♪

27:56.460 --> 27:58.380
[ Sighs ]

27:58.380 --> 28:05.330
♪♪

28:05.330 --> 28:12.250
♪♪

