Okay, everyone. We've
done this a thousand times.

28:13.920 --> 28:15.250
We know what to do.

28:15.250 --> 28:17.290
♪ A love like ours
will never die ♪

28:17.290 --> 28:19.250
Ten blade.

28:19.250 --> 28:21.790
♪♪

28:21.790 --> 28:24.250
♪ Never die ♪

28:24.250 --> 28:31.580
