DeLuca: What is all that?

28:39.460 --> 28:41.460
Link: Mostly sludge.

28:41.460 --> 28:43.420
I've never seen
this much tissue damage

28:43.420 --> 28:46.500
from a hip replacement before.

28:46.500 --> 28:48.580
Look at this
gluteus medius tendon.

28:48.580 --> 28:49.790
I can't believe
that was all inside of him.

28:49.790 --> 28:51.380
Not just him.

28:51.380 --> 28:53.380
These hips were the new
standard for a while.

28:53.380 --> 28:55.790
[ Grunts ] Surgeons used to
beg their hospitals

28:55.790 --> 28:57.170
to invest in them,

28:57.170 --> 29:01.750
but, uh, if this is happening
to other people...

29:01.750 --> 29:02.880
it's gonna be
a game-changer, DeLuca.

29:04.920 --> 29:06.540
Can someone get me
an update on Amelia?

29:06.540 --> 29:10.040
♪♪

29:10.040 --> 29:11.120
Amelia: Ooh.

29:11.120 --> 29:12.500
Okay.

29:12.500 --> 29:15.210
Oh. [ Sighs ]

29:15.210 --> 29:16.120
How are we doing?

29:16.120 --> 29:17.920
Uh, contractions are

29:17.920 --> 29:19.000
less than
three minutes apart.

29:19.000 --> 29:20.380
She's doing great.

29:20.380 --> 29:22.540
Ooh.
Good.
Can I take a look?

29:22.540 --> 29:24.120
Uh-huh. Ooh!

29:24.120 --> 29:25.500
I feel like my organs
are in a vice.

29:25.500 --> 29:27.170
[ Chuckles ]
Aah!

29:27.170 --> 29:29.540
Hey, I know you said
no medications, but --

29:29.540 --> 29:30.790
There's fentanyl
in the epidural.

29:30.790 --> 29:33.540
Nobody advertises that,
but -- Aah!

29:33.540 --> 29:36.210
[ Exhales sharply ]
Women are smart.

29:36.210 --> 29:38.000
We are evolved.
We are critical-thinking.

29:38.000 --> 29:40.420
How did the first woman
ever have a baby

29:40.420 --> 29:41.710
and then decide
to have another one?

29:41.710 --> 29:44.710
Aah!
Or let another woman have one?

29:44.710 --> 29:46.500
Oh.
How do humans exist?

29:46.500 --> 29:48.750
Why do we do this?

29:48.750 --> 29:53.210
You do this because
you're so in love with someone

29:53.210 --> 29:55.420
that the two of you
can't contain it all.

29:55.420 --> 29:58.460
So you make another person
out of that love.

29:58.460 --> 30:00.540
[ Sighs ]

30:00.540 --> 30:02.620
Oh, God.

30:02.620 --> 30:06.170
Bailey...I am so sorry.

30:06.170 --> 30:08.040
I'm awful.
I was not thinking about it.

30:08.040 --> 30:09.330
You can go.

30:09.330 --> 30:11.120
I ju-- I deserve to
have this baby on my own.

30:11.120 --> 30:12.920
D-- No.

30:12.920 --> 30:17.120
Now, that would go against
the rules of pregnancy club.

30:17.120 --> 30:18.880
[ Exhales sharply ]

30:18.880 --> 30:20.500
The surgery went well,

30:20.500 --> 30:22.790
and the bandages should be
able to come off soon.

30:22.790 --> 30:24.210
Recovery will be slow.

30:24.210 --> 30:27.000
You'll need rehab
and speech therapy.

30:27.000 --> 30:30.120
See, Dad?
Everything was fine.

30:30.120 --> 30:31.920
[ Footsteps approach ]

30:31.920 --> 30:33.460
I came as fast as I could.
Hi.

30:33.460 --> 30:34.540
How is she doing?

30:34.540 --> 30:37.710
Um...uh...we're great.

30:37.710 --> 30:39.830
Ms. Scott?

30:39.830 --> 30:42.920
Why are you here?

30:42.920 --> 30:45.290
I -- I was in
the neighborhood,

30:45.290 --> 30:48.170
and I thought
maybe you might

30:48.170 --> 30:50.790
want to catch up
on your homework.

30:50.790 --> 30:52.170
Oh, my God.

30:52.170 --> 30:54.750
Dad, you're dating
my algebra teacher?

30:54.750 --> 30:56.790
Um...only kind of.

30:56.790 --> 30:58.330
It's just...
[ Sighs ]

30:58.330 --> 31:00.420
We have the same dentist.
She set us up.

31:00.420 --> 31:02.460
I didn't know she was
your teacher at the time.

31:02.460 --> 31:04.920
We didn't want to tell you until
after the school year was over

31:04.920 --> 31:08.210
and you weren't
in my class.

31:08.210 --> 31:10.670
Oh, honey. Please.
Don't be upset.

31:10.670 --> 31:13.710
I'm not upset.
I'm trying to smile.

31:13.710 --> 31:15.500
[ Chuckles ]

31:15.500 --> 31:16.790
Okay.

31:19.880 --> 31:22.620
Well, now we know why
the dad never swiped right.

31:22.620 --> 31:24.790
God, I hate set-ups.

31:24.790 --> 31:26.000
But if it makes
them happy...

31:26.000 --> 31:28.460
[ Chuckles ]

31:28.460 --> 31:30.460
So, this lack of interest
in dating --

31:30.460 --> 31:32.250
it's...it's only in regards
to yourself, right?

31:32.250 --> 31:33.790
I mean,
just because I'm miserable

31:33.790 --> 31:35.670
doesn't mean
everyone else has to be.

31:35.670 --> 31:38.120
Okay.
So, I'm not wrong, then?

31:38.120 --> 31:39.790
'Cause I get the feeling
people are having conversations

31:39.790 --> 31:42.710
about my personal life
that I'm not privy to.

31:42.710 --> 31:44.250
You know,
you should smile more.

31:47.460 --> 31:49.460
Hmm.

31:49.460 --> 31:52.040
Ohh!
Okay,
it's time to push.

31:52.040 --> 31:53.670
Okay.
No, I ca--
I can't push anymore!

31:53.670 --> 31:55.250
I can't! I can't!
Oh, yes, you can.

31:55.250 --> 31:57.380
No, I can't! I'm done!
I'm dying! I can't!

31:57.380 --> 31:58.920
Okay, okay, but --
but think of

31:58.920 --> 32:00.580
all those women you were
talking about,

32:00.580 --> 32:01.540
the women that do this
every day.
[ Groaning ]

32:01.540 --> 32:03.170
No, I hate those women!

32:03.170 --> 32:05.080
And they all have drugs
and masturbation and --

32:05.080 --> 32:06.290
and then C-sections,

32:06.290 --> 32:07.420
and I don't even have Link!

32:07.420 --> 32:08.460
Ohhh!

32:08.460 --> 32:11.040
Uh, okay.

32:11.040 --> 32:12.170
Okay, here.
Sit up.

32:12.170 --> 32:13.540
I can't! I can't!
I can't do this!

32:13.540 --> 32:15.920
Okay. Tucker's father
wasn't with me, either.

32:15.920 --> 32:17.920
So, move.
Why?
What are you doing?

32:17.920 --> 32:20.000
Ah. Okay.
Okay.

32:20.000 --> 32:22.120
Oh, my God.
I can't do this.

32:22.120 --> 32:24.330
♪ Every breath ♪
Okay. Okay.

32:24.330 --> 32:25.620
Okay.
Now...

32:25.620 --> 32:27.420
Alright.
...let's have a baby.

32:27.420 --> 32:29.170
Okay.
One, two, three.
Okay.

32:29.170 --> 32:31.170
Push!
[ Screaming ]

32:31.170 --> 32:34.210
