34:24.670 --> 34:26.750
Yes! Sorry.

34:26.750 --> 34:27.920
[ Chuckles ]
[ Sighs ]

34:27.920 --> 34:29.250
Pierce, you can --
you can go if you need to.

34:29.250 --> 34:30.460
What? No.

34:30.460 --> 34:31.830
No, I do my best work

34:31.830 --> 34:34.620
