profoundly relieved.

34:34.620 --> 34:36.750
[ Exhales sharply ]

34:36.750 --> 34:38.460
Now, what about you? Don't you
have a wedding to get to?

34:38.460 --> 34:40.670
Ah, there's plenty of wine
to keep people happy.

34:40.670 --> 34:41.960
[ Cellphone chimes ]

34:41.960 --> 34:43.210
Oh, Schmitt, could you...?

34:43.210 --> 34:44.460
Oh. I'm doing yours
now, too?

34:44.460 --> 34:45.790
Great.

34:45.790 --> 34:47.670
Great use
