34:50.290 --> 34:51.500
Could you just, uh,
put it on speaker?

34:51.500 --> 34:53.380
Yep.
Thanks.
Teddy: Oh.

34:53.380 --> 34:55.290
Mm. [ Breathing heavily ]

34:55.290 --> 34:57.580
Oh.

34:57.580 --> 34:59.420
Oh, God.

34:59.420 --> 35:01.250
Oh, God.

35:01.250 --> 35:02.830
Schmitt?
Oh, yes!

35:02.830 --> 35:03.920
Schmitt.
Yep. Yep.

35:03.920 --> 35:05.250
Schmitt!
Yep, yep, yeah!

35:05.250 --> 35:05.920
I'm trying, I'm trying,
I'm trying, I'm tr--

35:05.920 --> 35:07.120
Okay.

35:12.040 --> 35:14.880
