S-Sorry, everyone.

35:14.880 --> 35:16.380
Clearly,
that was meant for me.

35:16.380 --> 35:17.710
[ Laughter ]

35:17.710 --> 35:19.620
You know, Teddy's idea
of a wedding gift.

35:19.620 --> 35:22.080
Yeah.
Yeah, that's a good one.

35:22.080 --> 35:23.080
Yeah.
Yeah.

35:23.080 --> 35:24.580
Um...suc-- Um --

35:24.580 --> 35:27.080
