35:45.580 --> 35:47.880
I'm okay.

35:47.880 --> 35:49.210
Everything's okay.

35:49.210 --> 35:50.460
[ Baby cooing ]

35:50.460 --> 35:54.670
Atticus Lincoln...
come meet your son.

35:54.670 --> 35:57.290
