hazy scene ♪

35:57.290 --> 35:59.120
[ Exhales sharply ]

35:59.120 --> 36:00.960
Oh, my God.

36:00.960 --> 36:02.620
[ Baby fusses ]

36:02.620 --> 36:05.000
Oh, my God. Hi.

36:05.000 --> 36:06.210
Oh.

36:06.210 --> 36:07.920
♪ With my head up
in the sky ♪

36:07.920 --> 36:09.170
Hi.

36:09.170 --> 36:10.500
♪ I am free ♪
Oh, oh.

36:10.500 --> 36:12.120
He's so small.

36:12.120 --> 36:14.120
Don't say that to the person
who just pushed him out.

36:14.120 --> 36:16.380
♪ ...and who I want to be ♪

36:16.380 --> 36:18.830
♪ And who I want to be,
I want to be ♪

36:18.830 --> 36:21.880
♪ I know just what I want to
know, just where I want to go ♪

36:21.880 --> 36:24.000
♪ And who I want to be ♪

36:24.000 --> 36:25.080
♪ I want to be ♪

